{"tid":2500614,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"傳謝安琪加盟ViuTV做一姐 將同老公張繼聰打對台","createTime":"2021-04-22T19:56:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T21:46:08.000Z","uid":130626,"like":10,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ae352be6999b61cf99cdf6010ca7d171b2af274b","tid":2500614,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T19:56:43.000Z","msg":"謝安琪自從約滿Juno後，大家都非常關心她的新動向，今日有報導指謝安琪將會加盟ViuTV成為一姐，先會開劇令她再度成為女一，而ViuTV的姊妹公司大國文化，亦會為謝安琪出碟及開演唱會，該報導指ViuTV打算以這三樣條件利誘謝安琪加盟，不過ViuTV製作部副總裁金廣誠受訪時，只表示有節目找謝安琪合作，但是否加盟成為ViuTV一份子，就沒有正面答覆，只表示ViuTV大門是開放的。<br />\n<br />\n而謝安琪丈夫張繼聰最近經常在TVB出現，更上了兩個綜藝節目，分別是《勁歌金曲》及《開心大綜藝》，該報導指張繼聰跟TVB越走越近，但張繼聰早前接受《香港01》訪問時，表示今年的時間表，已留給在電影工作，應該沒有空檔拍攝劇集，但跟王祖藍一直保持聯絡及關係友好。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210423/462085038880591872203741.jpeg/RBUmBx6IDejoUwqEi_-fj1T1p8cddXy3QJDTw0CQ08M?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210423%2F462085038880591872203741.jpeg%2FRBUmBx6IDejoUwqEi_-fj1T1p8cddXy3QJDTw0CQ08M%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=2d06b4c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2dae3273c77e5a37e513e5e0537a5e7d3cd28596","tid":2500614,"uid":13421,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T19:57:52.000Z","msg":"食兩家茶禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1327f97990f45c32116d537d5410a81d36c25804","tid":2500614,"uid":42364,"like":15,"dislike":7,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T20:02:33.000Z","msg":"你兩公婆死開啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n謝繼聰細佬做狗架<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ad87868c1171e9ca6b5d48fb229aa203e1d25e","tid":2500614,"uid":244361,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T20:05:36.000Z","msg":"唔關黃藍事但唔知點解越嚟越唔鐘意呢兩公婆"},{"pid":"295619d8e75342e224db78500896ebcbaf2d2484","tid":2500614,"uid":7854,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T20:07:59.000Z